----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Asset Usage & Permission

You may not share, leak, or redistribute any internal assets such as source code, UI designs, or backend scripts from BloxOLite.
Use of these assets in your own games is strictly forbidden unless you have written permission from the Owner (FJFG11). 


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


2. Tampering & Obfuscation

Obfuscated scripts (e.g., Server_Manager) are protected. Bypassing, reverse engineering, or tampering with verification systems is strictly prohibited and will result in immediate license termination.

If you discover a vulnerability or exploit, report it responsibly by joining our server and opening a support ticket. Following our Responsible Disclosure policy ensures your license remains safe.


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


3. Refund Policy

BloxOLite does not offer refunds under any circumstances. All sales are final.


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


4. Redistribution

You are not allowed to redistribute any BloxOLite assets, including but not limited to UI files, scripts, or modules. Redistribution in any form (paid or free) will lead to license revocation and potential blacklisting.


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


5. Asset Requests / Begging

Requesting assets from current BloxOLite users (e.g., "Can you send me the MAES?") is strictly prohibited.
If a user shares assets with you, both parties will have their licenses permanently revoked for violating these Terms.


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


6. Responsible Disclosure

BloxOLite prioritizes the security and integrity of its systems and assets. If you are a developer or security researcher who has found a legitimate vulnerability, we encourage you to report it responsibly.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


7. Appeals

If your license was revoked and you believe it was in error, you may open a support ticket with proof and a valid reason.

Note: We currently do not offer an appeal system for bans outside of the official BloxOLite Discord server. You may contact staff directly, but we reserve the right to ignore appeals that don't follow proper channels.


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


8. Legal Notice

BloxOLite reserves the right to:
Update or change these Terms at any time
Deny access to products or support to users who break our rules
Enforce legal action in cases of asset theft, redistribution, or fraud
By using BloxOLite, you accept these Terms and agree to follow all policies and procedures outlined above.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

By purchasing or using any assets from BloxOLite, you automatically agree to the following Terms of Service. Failure to comply may result in your license being revoked without refund or warning.

